title: Stocks to Watch: What's Ahead for the Markets
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin speaks with deputy editor Ben Levisohn and Doug Peta, chief strategist, U.S. Investment Strategy at BCA Research, on the outlook for financial markets, Fed policy, corporate earnings, and individual stocks.
